content: I'm excited to try out some of these crunchy snack alternatives! The roasted chickpeas and kale chips sound like great options, and I love the idea of making my own granola at home. Speaking of homemade snacks, I recently tried making my own granola for the first time and it turned out amazing. I've been snacking on it throughout the day, and it's been great to have on hand. Do you have any other homemade snack recipes you could share? Maybe something with nuts or seeds?
